				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/C%E1%BB%91c-phong-1/poem-XYePkru28YnTrWz9ZKV57w">Cốc phong 1 - 穀風 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/D%E1%BB%A5-ch%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%B3-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-h%E1%BB%8Bch-v%C4%83n/poem-j9Hfw5Qp2ojck3M3yZbHSw">Dụ chư tỳ tướng hịch văn - 諭諸裨將檄文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-B3gaZnYZj3Y7n162MsC6mQ">Trần Quốc Tuấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Phanh/Minh-nguy%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B7-h%E1%BB%93i-m%C3%A3n/poem-NdqTCFjd0f1UQi16Tk2Xsw">Minh nguyệt kỷ hồi mãn - 明月幾回滿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Phanh/author-KzYYRRdpC3C-h8YlLpfBMA">Phạm Phanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%C3%A1t-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-C%E1%BB%91c-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-VmdDx8oi1-YcvXe8X2T_Ww">Phát Đồng Cốc huyện - 發同谷縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-B%C3%A1c/Thanh-minh-h%E1%BA%ADu-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-T%E1%BA%A7n-so%C3%A1i-%C4%90oan-Minh-h%E1%BB%99i-%E1%BA%A9m-L%C3%BD-th%E1%BB%8B-vi%C3%AAn-tr%C3%AC-ng%E1%BA%ABu-t%C3%A1c/poem-QOzXGPvCsFOaL6xQ_FnCGw">Thanh minh hậu đồng Tần soái Đoan Minh hội ẩm Lý thị viên trì ngẫu tác - 清明後同秦帥端明會飲李氏園池偶作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-B%C3%A1c/author-3f-_gwzHi_bamfFWfl14VQ">Văn Ngạn Bác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ACnh/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-k%C3%BD-Ho%C3%A0ng-Ph%E1%BB%A7-Nhi%E1%BB%85m-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Phong/poem-DrWqaXWV8a-sCjoEnxpAdg">Thu dạ ký Hoàng Phủ Nhiễm, Trịnh Phong - 秋夜寄皇甫冉鄭豐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ACnh/author-muwOXCdrb6me3mNm5PEtLQ">Lưu Phương Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BA%BFt/Thung-L%C4%83ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-p2nhZFT0UlZaSH48t6Kosw">Thung Lăng hành - 舂陵行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BA%BFt/author-9Y30zD24BFXrRqipoBvcFA">Nguyên Kết</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem--LsKiQ1eOygSMk7fNhUr8w">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ nhị đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第二段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/T%E1%BB%91ng-T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-s%C4%A9-du-Thi%C3%AAn-Thai/poem-VYPpc_6MU3XP1rW0Osh2UA">Tống Tư Mã đạo sĩ du Thiên Thai - 送司馬道士遊天台</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-ugO5moh7gzYYDOe2gVJzDg">Tống Chi Vấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Long-V%C3%A2n/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Minh-Qu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-roASAGoyDtlpxUEQvmAeVg">Vương Minh Quân kỳ 2 - 王明君其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Long-V%C3%A2n/author-nyAygBBUwiX2rbZbi_xZ-Q">Lư Long Vân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
